title: Red Ninja End of Honor- xbox 1-

This is my personal first iso I have ever attempted to make, and it worked. Red ninja   is pretty much your basic ninja assassination game, with constant panty shots to keep you happy. This game is for the first Xbox, not 360, but is might work on a modded 360 anyway.
